findings.title: Owner can withdraw marketing balance
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw the marketing balance, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can disable auto call of _swapContractToken function
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to disable the automatic calling of the _swapContractToken function.

findings.title: Owner can change antiWhale
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the antiWhale setting.

findings.title: Owner can change teamWallet and ConstructionWallet addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify teamWallet and ConstructionWallet addresses, which could lead to unauthorized changes.

findings.title: Owner can disable buy lock
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to disable the buy lock feature.

findings.title: Owner can change currentAmountToSwap
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the current amount to swap, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can exclude addresses
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude addresses.

findings.title: Owner can change buy lock time
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the buy lock time, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change taxes
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify tax settings.

findings.title: Owner can manually call _swapContractToken function
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to manually call the _swapContractToken function, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change PancakeRouter address
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the PancakeRouter address, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can change balance and sell limits
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify balance and sell limits, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can enable trading(already called)
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to enable trading, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can change liquidity token address
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the liquidity token address.

findings.title: Owner can increase _liquidityUnlockTime
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to increase the _liquidityUnlockTime variable.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw liquidity to team wallet if it is not locked
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw liquidity to the team wallet when it's not locked.

findings.title: Owner can remove liquidity
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to remove liquidity from the contract.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract balance if it is not locked
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to withdraw the contract's balance when it is not locked.
